        <div class="aboutcontent">
            <blockquote>
                I knew with a sinking heart that we where going to talk equipment. I could just see it coming. I hate talking equipment. "So what made you buy a Gregory pack?" he said. "Well, I thought it would be easier than carrying everything in my arms."
                </blockquote>
            <cite>&#8213; Bill Bryson - A Walk in the Woods</cite> 
            <div class="about_text"><p>Well, honestly i'm very much into equipment and i'm carrying far too much stuff around the planet. We'll see if i need it.</p>
            <p><small>Updated 22.July 2010</small></p>
